high_descs: Turn to your right and step forward then turn left and and walk to the counter that is on your left past the fridge
Pick up the lettuce that is sitting on the counter
Turn around and take a step from the counter then turn right and walk to the fridge that is on your right.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the middle shelf then close the door.  Open the fridge and pick up the lettuce from the middle shelf
Turn left and walk to the sink on your right
Place the lettuce into the sink
anns.task_desc: Place chilled lettuce into a sink

high_descs: Turn right, take several steps, and then turn left to find the toaster on the counter to your left.
Pick up the lettuce next to the toaster.
Take a step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right and walk towards the sink on your right.
Place the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the cooled lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Go to the left around the fridge and head to the counter right of the fridge.
Pick up the lettuce on the counter.
Bring the lettuce to the fridge on the left.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Head right with the chilled lettuce and go to the sink on the right.
Put the chilled lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce in the sink.
